These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, collecting, sudoku, magic-tricks
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, volleyball, swimming, skiing
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
3. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##8
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is not the person who's hobby is sudoku##6
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks  | puzzles | sudoku | collecting  |
| Sport   | cricket | swimming   | skiing  | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, pineapple, cauliflower, banana
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, bartender, videographer, dancer
1. the dancer is not to the left of the dancer##8
2. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the right of the person eating banana##5
3. the person eating lemon is the bartender##1
4. the person eating banana is between the person eating lemon and the person eating pineapple##2
5. the person eating pineapple is somewhere between the person eating cauliflower and the entrepreneur##7
6. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
7. the entrepreneur is not to the left of the entrepreneur##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | cauliflower | pineapple          | banana | lemon     |
| Job    | videographer      | dancer | entrepreneur | bartender |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, journalist, photographer, manager
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, crime, sports, documentary
1. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the photographer##8
2. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1
3. the journalist is on the right of the videographer##1
4. the journalist is in an even position##4
5. the manager is on the far left or far right##3
6. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
7. the manager is the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | videographer | journalist | photographer     | manager |
| Movie-Genre   | crime    | documentary   | fantasy | sports    |

