.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, reggae, ambient, classical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, swimming, rugby, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##8
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
4. the fan of classical is not to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##8
5. the fan of r&b is the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
7. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the left of the fan of classical##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | reggae         | classical   | r&b    |
| Sport         | swimming | volleyball | rugby | badminton |

