.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, animation, disaster, time-travel
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, water-polo, cricket, ice-hockey
1. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person watching animation movies##7
2. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
3. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
4. the person watching disaster movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere between the person watching animation movies and the person who's sport is water-polo##7
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##5
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
8. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation   | disaster | time-travel | martial-arts    |
| Sport         | skiing | ice-hockey   | cricket   | water-polo |

