4. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
5. the person eating apple is somewhere to the left of the person eating peas##5
6. the person eating orange is not to the left of the fan of classical##8
7. the person eating orange is the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
