.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, juice, milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, water-polo, cycling, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person who's sport is cycling##7
3. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##8
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
7. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea      | juice | hot-chocolate | milk   |
| Sport      | climbing | cycling | skateboarding  | water-polo |

