3. the freelancer is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the freelancer##7
5. the analyst is not to the right of the security-guard##8
6. the security-guard is somewhere between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the analyst##7

.:: Answer ::.
