.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, punk, r&b, disco
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, roller, bike, airplane
1. the fan of ambient is between the fan of disco and the person driving the jet-ski##2
2. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
4. the fan of punk is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5
5. the person driving the roller is the person driving the roller##1
6. the fan of r&b is not the person driving the bike##6
7. the fan of disco is not to the right of the fan of r&b##8
8. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the left of the person driving the roller##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | ambient | r&b | punk |
| Transport     | airplane | roller       | jet-ski  | bike    |

