.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, pepper, watermelon, mango
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, cooking, rock-climbing, dancing
1. the person eating watermelon is not to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the right of the person eating pepper##8
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating watermelon is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
6. the person eating pepper is on the far left##1
7. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | pepper        | mango | watermelon      | raspberry    |
| Hobby   | gardening | rock-climbing   | cooking | dancing |

