.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, lemonade, water
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, soccer, basketball
1. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##8
2. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere between the person who's sport is soccer and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
8. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water | hot-chocolate         | lemonade    | almond-milk       |
| Sport      | surfing | basketball | baseball | soccer |

