.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, cabbage, kiwi, potato
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, time-travel, fantasy, scientific
 1. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##5
 2. the person eating potato is not to the left of the person eating kiwi##8
 3. the person eating lettuce is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##8
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating kiwi##5
 7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating lettuce is not to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##8
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is not to the left of the person eating lettuce##8
10. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | cabbage    | kiwi | lettuce | potato |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | scientific  | fantasy     | time-travel    |

