.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, radish, watermelon, kiwi
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, rock-climbing, hiking, dancing
1. the person eating watermelon is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person eating watermelon is not to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##8
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person eating kiwi##1
5. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating radish##1
6. the person eating radish is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person eating kiwi##2
7. the person eating watermelon is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
