.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, lizard, mouse, horse
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, subway, motorbike, bus
1. the owner of the horse is not the person driving the motorbike##6
2. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
3. the owner of the lizard is somewhere between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the horse##7
4. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
5. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
6. the person driving the van is not to the right of the person driving the subway##8
7. the owner of the lizard is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | goat  | horse | lizard  | mouse  |
| Transport   | van | subway   | bus | motorbike |

