.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, fish, turtle
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, motorbike, tram
1. the person driving the helicopter is not the owner of the ferret##6
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
3. the owner of the turtle is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
4. the owner of the fish is the person driving the bike##1
5. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the bike##7
6. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is between the person driving the tram and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | lizard    | turtle | ferret | fish |
| Transport   | helicopter | tram      | motorbike     | bike     |

 